", "id": "1593305657751911", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974576_1593305661085244_1368760051307669731_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=nMzB6fwZrFUQ7kNvgHXDHVT&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDRGdnpJowHQPobBbT7nbWr5x_wSdcmY-hCgcnXQz-e7A&oe=67595F61"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "PVR_Cover Landscape - 2560x1440.png", "id": "429997232540328", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75361360_429997235873661_5804819608709080672_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=UHBJKEi7Oq4Q7kNvgGCPdjC&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBddJT50rAr5sJFOHwcgIMRfwAWm4jZJU0bmldZD3k9LQ&oe=67596AC8"}, "display_name": "Programmer VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Want to learn programming in a fun way? \n\nLook no further than Programmer VR\n\nHelp Bob collect rewards by overcoming obstacles in 3 breathtaking virtual worlds.  Learn programming concepts, sharpen your logical thinking and develop problem-solving skills in an easy, fun, immersive, and enjoyable way. This game is brought to you by the developers of iB Cricket, one of the highest-rated VR games.\n\nKey features:\n- 50 levels of programming fun\n- 3 enchanting virtual worlds -  Pond, Futuristic Neon City, and Neon Pyramid\n- No previous programming knowledge is required\n- Sharpen your logical thinking skills and improve your critical thinking skills\n- Learn programming concepts like Instruction execution order,  Conditional Statements, and Loops.\n- Co-op Mode\n", "short_description": "Help Bob collect rewards by overcoming obstacles in 3 breathtaking virtual worlds. As you help Bob progress through 50 levels, you\u2019ll learn programming concepts, sharpen your logical thinking and develop problem-solving skills in an easy, fun, immersive, and enjoyable way."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://proyuga.tech/programmer-vr-privacy-po